    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "you mentioned there a consensus that it's a net positive for gdp... but isn't that debatable? like, some people argue it actually hurts the economy by putting too much pressure on local resources and driving down pay for low-skilled workers. why is the benefit considered more of a consensus than the risks?",
